  "decision_conditions": [
    "The cumulative width of the existing and proposed single storey rear extension would have a width greater than half the width of the original dwelling house and therefore would not comply with permitted development as outlined under Schedule 2, Part 1, Class A of The Town and Country Planning (General Permitted Development) (England) Order 2015 and the MHCLG Permitted development rights for householders Technical Guidance (September 2019).",
